This folder contains all the source codes from O-BBNIP2. To replicate the experiments, edit the 
"main_Problem2_Opt.py" file to change the input instance file names (make sure to add the complete path to the network file or to add
the network file to the same folder). Also, make sure to scroll down the "main_Problem2.Opt" file to edit/update
the names of the result files according to your experiments.
